I want to help people. I want to work with kids who have been hurt.  I want to help families who have problems. I think social work is a good way to do this. I will work for the Division of Family and Children Services.

I know that social workers need to be kind and helpful. They need to do the right thing. They need to want to help people get along. I want to be a good social worker. I want to learn new things and get better at my job. These things are important to me.

I always wanted to help others. When I was in school, I saw people who had problems. Some people tried to hide their problems. Some people used bad ways to deal with their problems. I saw these things and decided to study psychology. 

After I finished college, I took a break. One day I met a boy. He was scared. His parents were bad to him. He asked my friend for help. I went to talk to the boy’s parents. I told the police my ideas. The police asked me to talk to the parents. The parents were nervous. They said bad things about their son.

This made me want to be a social worker. I want to help kids like this boy.

Another thing that is important to me is fairness. We say that everyone is important. But we do not always treat everyone fairly. I like to be myself. I like to be different.

In school, I stood up for what is right. I showed that I cared about fairness. I will always fight for fairness.

This paper talks about two ways to look at insomnia: the biological way and the sociocultural way. The biological way looks at genes and medical things. The sociocultural way looks at how people's lives and groups they are in affect sleep. 

This paper looks at these ways and talks about some research. It also says what is good and bad about each piece of research.

Insomnia is a sleep problem. There are different kinds of sleep problems. Some are problems with falling asleep or staying asleep. Some are problems with bad dreams or acting out dreams. Some are caused by other mental health problems or medical problems.

This paper is mostly about insomnia and sleep problems in general.

The biological way looks at genes, family history, and how the body works. Some parts of the brain control sleep and wakefulness. One study looked at mice and found that a part of the brain called the hypothalamus has special parts called GABAB receptors. These receptors help control sleep.

When these receptors work well, they help people sleep. If they don't work well, people may have trouble sleeping. This shows that there are both genes and things in the environment that can affect sleep.

The sociocultural way looks at how people's lives and groups they belong to affect sleep. For example, stress, work, and family life can all affect sleep. This means that people who are stressed, have demanding jobs, or have problems in their families may have more trouble sleeping.

This paper talks about three things about Central Auditory Processing Disorder (CAPD). First, it gives a short meaning of the problem. Next, it talks about how doctors find out if someone has CAPD. Finally, it talks about what a teacher in a normal school can do to help a student with CAPD.

Central Auditory Processing Disorder (CAPD), or Auditory Processing Disorder (APD) means how good the brain is at using the sounds it hears. It is when the brain does not work well to understand sounds. People with CAPD can hear sounds, but their brain has trouble understanding them. The brain does not work well to separate words or to tell what sounds to focus on.

The first time people talked about this problem was in the 1950s. They called it “auditory imperception”. Doctors started to test children to see if they had this problem. In 1977, a big meeting was held to talk about CAPD.

CAPD can show up in many ways. Some people with CAPD have trouble knowing where a sound is coming from. Some people have trouble telling the difference between two sounds. Some people have trouble hearing patterns in sounds. Some people have trouble understanding what someone means by their voice.

To find out if someone has CAPD, doctors use tests. These tests see how well a person hears and understands sounds. There is no one test that is always good at finding CAPD. There is no known reason why people have CAPD.

The play Twelfth Night show that masks are good for tricks. But in the end, a person must be true to themself. If not, they will lose themself. 

It is hard to stop a trick. Some people will be mad. They will not like being tricked. A person must choose between being themself or keeping friends.

Masks and being someone else are hard. It is hard to know why a person wants to hide. Why does Viola want to be a man? She is safe as a man. She says: “I’ll bring you to a captain in this town/Where lie my maiden weeds, by whose gentle help/ I was preserved to serve this noble count…” (5.1.247-249)

Being a man helps Viola. But it makes her lonely. She misses women. Then Olivia likes Viola/Cesario. Olivia says: “Whither, my lord? Cesario, husband, stay.” (5.1.138)

Viola also likes Orsino. Orsino says: “Boy, thou hast said to me a thousand times/ Thou never shouldst love woman like to me.” (5.1. 260-261)

Twelfth Night shows how tricks can help us know our feelings. Olivia and Orsino like Viola. But do they like her as a man or a woman? 

Olivia likes Sebastian too. She changes her mind easily. She sees Viola as a sister, not a lover. She says: “A sister, you are she.” (5.1.315)

German rule in some areas had bad times. This is true for the Ovaherero and Nama people in German South West Africa. But, not all of German rule was like this. The German empire was big and had many different parts. The same was true for how they taught people.

Some places, like German East Africa, had lots of schools run by the government. When Britain took over, they saw many Africans who could read and write. This was not true in South West Africa. 

Here, the church taught most people. The government did not help much. The government did help Europeans learn. They built schools just for them. 

This made a big difference. In other places, many Africans could read. But not in South West Africa. Most people there could not read or write. 

Why was this? This paper will look at the reasons. We will talk about what people who lived there thought about Africans.

Popular music has many types. There are many kinds of music today. Rock, pop, jazz, country, and rap are some kinds. Each type has many small types too. Heavy metal is one type that has many small types. Heavy metal music is very strong. It has loud sounds and fast music.

People like heavy metal because it shows strong feelings. Heavy metal music has many ideas and sounds. It is different from other music. 

Heavy metal music has many parts. Some parts are quiet. Some parts are very loud. Heavy metal music is from a time when people liked to use strong drugs. The music is dark and loud. It is different from earlier music.

Heavy metal music is still very popular. People like to listen to it. Heavy metal music is a way for people to show their feelings.

Henri Rousseau was a painter. He had a dream. His dream was to be a good painter. He wanted other people to like his art. This was hard.  He did not go to art school. He worked for the government. He started to paint when he was a grown man. 

Rousseau’s art was very different. He painted things in a simple way. He liked to paint dreams and jungle scenes. Other artists liked to paint in new and modern ways. Rousseau wanted to be like them. He wanted to be part of the art world.

He made a painting called “The Dream.” It shows a woman in a jungle. She is looking at the world around her. This painting shows Rousseau’s dream. He wanted to be a good artist. He wanted to be accepted.

Rousseau was a man of simple dreams. He wanted to be good at something. He wanted to be part of something bigger than himself. His painting shows this.

Many smart people think that good things and good art are connected. I think they are right. One poet, John Keats, said, "Beauty is truth, truth beauty- That is all / Ye know on earth, and all ye need to know."

We learn much from school or life. But we seem to know good things and good art without learning. Good things and good art are like tries to explain things, not tell us what to do.

We study good art and good things to understand why they are good. We do not have rules to say what is good art or good.

We can talk about art, but we can not say why it is good. People say, "There's just something about it" when they like something.

Art and good things can not be fully explained. A story is like this. A story can say things that we can not say in words.

Ethics, or good things, are like this too. We can not fully explain good things.

I think good things and good art are connected because we feel them deeply. They are more than words can say.

Literature is special because it has good things in it. We need good things in life.

Germany is a strong country. It has many different cultures. These cultures are in many places. They are from the mountains in Munich to the sea in Kiel. They are also in the city of Cologne on the Rhine River, in the center of Germany, and in Dresden on the Elbe River. Germany is made up of many different parts.

The name Germany comes from a group of people called the Germans.  Historians do not know for sure where the name came from.  Tacitus, a Roman writer, said the name came from a group called the Tungrians. They were in Germany before they fought the Gauls. Julius Caesar, a Roman general, used the word “Germanus” to talk about people he fought in the Gallic Wars. He used it to show the difference between the Gauls he conquered and the Germans he did not. Some people think “Germanus” came from the Gauls.

Tacitus wrote about the Germans in his book, “De Origine et situ Germanorum”. He said that the Germans were the first people in that land. He said they did not mix with other people.


The Romans did not want to live in Germany. They fought with the Germans for goods and land.

I look down. I see the thing in front of me. My mind works fast. It sees the thing. But it does not feel much. My mind is like water. It flows. It moves. It does not stay in one place. I try to think. But my thoughts go away quickly. 

A long time ago, an artist told me to read a book about drawing. The book is called “The New Drawing on the Right Side of the Brain.” I want to learn to draw. I want to do it since I was six years old. The book talks about how the brain sees shapes. It talks about lines. 

The book says to look at a picture. Then, put a box around it. The box makes the picture smaller. It makes it easier to see.

Now, I look at the thing. I see it is very full of details. I am very surprised. I feel small. Famous painters like Picasso and Monet, they had their own styles. I want to have my own style too. I want to call it "Work in Brown."

I pick up my tool. I am ready to make art. I use my hand. My hand is strong. It moves. The water is calm. It is clear.

Something breaks off. It goes away.

My hand moves again. It hits the toilet. The thing does not move. It is stuck.

I use a mop. I wear a green tie. It is tight. I look at the thing in the bowl. It is bad. Someone left it for me. I flush the toilet again. Then, I take toilet paper. I wrap it around my hand.

I stand up. I bend down. I put my hand in the bowl.

Many young people die in car crashes.  Many things cause this problem. The National Institutes of Health say that teen brains are not ready for driving.  They also have little experience.  This causes more crashes, rollovers, speeding, and driving off the road.

Teens are more dangerous when they have friends in the car.  The Southern California Injury Prevention Research Center studied this.

Some states make teen drivers get special licenses. These licenses limit driving hours and how many young people can be in the car.

But these licenses are not enough.  Young drivers are not ready for the risks of driving. Psychologist Marvin Zuckerman says 18 is too young for a regular license.  He says young people like risks.  It is better to wait until they are older.

We need new laws.  Schools can teach teens about driving.  But no one under 18 can drive.  Teens can get a special permit before they get a license. They also need to practice driving.

Many states require 6 hours of driving practice and 50 hours of practice with an adult.  We should have the same rules in all states. This will help keep teens safe.

I look at films by Edison. He made many short films with tricks. I see fifteen films made between 1895 and 1901. These films use tricks to show things that are not real. I look at how the films are made. I see how most of them are made the same way. 

Most of these films are made inside. They look like a stage. The camera does not move. The people in the films move side to side. They do not walk to or from the camera.  In the film *Uncle Josh in a Spooky Hotel*, the people walk back and forth. The camera does not follow them.

Most of the films use long shots. The camera shows the whole person. It does not use close-ups. This is like a stage show. The audience sees the whole show. 

Most of the films are one shot. One idea is shown in one shot. The films are short, about one minute long. They show tricks, like magic. 

Sometimes, the films use many shots to make one trick. For example, in *The Execution of Mary, Queen of Scots*, there is a trick with a head. The film seems like one shot, but it is made with many shots joined together.

John Taylor was a man who liked freedom. He worked on a farm and he was in government for a short time. He was known for saying what he thought, especially about how people should be free. He liked farming. He thought it was the best job. Most of his ideas about government came from his love of farming.

He wanted a government that helped farmers. He wanted rules that protected farms and helped farming grow. He thought the government should not be too big or powerful. He thought the government should not tell people what to do too much. 

He thought the new United States had a good chance to make a good government. There were no old ways to follow, so they could make something new. He thought people had rights that the government should not take away. He thought these rights were important for everyone.

He thought the government should be careful. He said people are good and bad. He thought the government should protect the good and stop the bad. He thought the government should help people be good and protect their farms. He thought the government should be small and not take too much money. 

He thought the people who made the Constitution were smart. He wanted the government to follow the rules in the Constitution. He thought it was important to follow the rules. He thought the Constitution was the most important rule book.

The numbers of people who used the commuter log went down a lot in the third month. This was sad. We do not know why this happened. In the winter, fewer people walk or bike to school. This may be one reason. December is the end of a school term. People are very busy with schoolwork. They may not have time to use the log. December is also the start of the holiday season. Many students and teachers are off for a month. They may not come to school at all. Classes start again in late January. This may be why there were few log entries in January. But this does not explain the low number in February.

Many projects start with a lot of energy. This energy may go down over time. To keep people using the log, we had a special week in March called the Carpool Challenge. This helped to increase the number of log entries. One challenge was keeping people interested in the project. This was hard because of the holiday breaks and the end of the school term.

Another challenge is that people like to drive their cars. This is part of our culture. We had to give out prizes to encourage people to use other ways to get to school. We gave out gift cards to stores and restaurants. It would be interesting to see if bigger prizes would have helped, such as a bike, a hybrid car, or an electric car.

The prizes did not change during the project. If the prizes were bigger over time, more people might have used the log. The gift cards were good at the start, but bigger prizes later might have helped.

An ETF is like a basket of stocks. You can buy it on the market, like a single stock. It lets you own many things at once. ETFs are good because they have low fees. They are also good for quick buys and sells.

An ETF follows a list of stocks, like an index. It is like a smaller version of a big group of stocks. People like ETFs because they are easy to use. They can sell part of an ETF, or sell the whole thing.  

One ETF, IHF, follows ten big stocks. Its goal is to match these stocks' gains and losses. But, is IHF truly better than owning these ten stocks alone?

To find out, we looked at the ten biggest stocks in IHF. They make up most of the ETF's value. We compared the returns and risks of owning these ten stocks to owning the whole ETF.

We found that owning the ten stocks directly gave a higher return. It was also slightly less risky. This means you might make more money and lose less.

But, we need to know if this difference is real or just luck. We looked at how much the stocks move up and down. We found that the ten stocks move less than IHF. 

So, owning the ten stocks might be better than owning IHF. It might give more return and less risk. But we need to be sure. We need to check if the difference is big enough to matter.

Edgar Allan Poe said “Dream-Land” is one of his best poems. In the poem, Poe uses the word “Thulé” two times.  Mabbott says Poe got the word from Virgil. Virgil used the word to talk about an island north of Britain. The Greeks thought it was the edge of the world. It is true that Virgil used the word. But Poe may have read a newer book. Poe liked German writers a lot. 

One writer is Goethe.  Karl J. Arndt wrote a book about Poe and Goethe. Arndt said Poe copied Goethe’s poem. 

The Oxford Companion to English Literature says Goethe wrote a famous play called *Faust*. It has two parts. The first part came out in 1808. The second part came out in 1832 when Goethe died. In the second part of *Faust* is a short poem called “The King of Thulé”. The king’s wife dies. She gave him a cup as a gift. He drinks a lot and cries for his wife. He thinks it is time to die. He gives his things to his children. He keeps the cup. He goes to a cliff, throws the cup into the ocean, closes his eyes, and dies. 

The king in “The King of Thulé” is similar to the speaker in “Dream-Land”. They are both sad. Maybe they both drink too much. *Faust* was made into a play in 1842. This was less than a year before Poe used the word “Thulé” in his poem “The Pit and the Pendulum”.

Poe used “Thulé” twice in his work. He used “ultma Thule” in “The Pit and the Pendulum”. He used “Thulé” twice in “Dream-Land”. “The King of Thulé” and “Dream-Land” are like matching poems. In “Dream-Land” the speaker talks about how dark and lonely Thulé is. He sees dead friends. He sees a world without color. This is like the king in “The King of Thulé” who is lonely and sad.

Goethe was a very important writer. Poe would have known about him. Poe liked Tennyson. When asked if he liked Tennyson, Poe said yes. Poe would have read Goethe’s work too. Many copies of Goethe’s work were made after it was first published.

A person can get hurt in a store. They can fall and get hurt. If the store did not make the store safe, the person can ask for more money. This extra money is called punitive damages. 

A judge may not say that a person cannot get punitive damages right away. To get this extra money, the person must show that the store manager did something very bad. The person must show that the manager knew that people could get hurt, but did not care. 

The person can say that the manager knew the store was dangerous. Other people had fallen before. The manager did not clean up the spill. 

The person can also say that the manager acted badly. This is harder to prove. But, many people fell, and the manager did not fix the problem.

One day, an employee told the manager about a spill. The manager said he was eating and did not have time. Another employee told him again. Still, he did not clean it up. Later, a person fell and was hurt.

In California, a person can get more money if the store acted badly. The store must have been very mean or did not care if people got hurt.

Four years ago, I took a class about Islam.  We talked a lot about if Islam is a bad religion. This is a big question now. After 9/11, the news showed Islam in a bad way. Now, the news is very nice to Islam. I do not think we could have had a president named Barack Obama if it happened before 9/11. Obama has family from Islam.
The story of Muhammad is interesting. My ideas about Muhammad were different before. I thought he was mean and forced people to be Muslim. He took over tribes and made them follow him. But the book says Muhammad was kind. He did not force people. People came to him.
I see some things in Muhammad’s story that are like Jesus. Like when he made food for many people. This makes me think the writers want people to think Muhammad is great. They want to make people think Muhammad is like Jesus. This is not good because it takes away from Jesus.
Many stories in the book have people talking about what other people said. For example, “So and so said that so and so said.” I do not like this because it makes the stories sound less true.
I do not like that the book makes Muhammad seem like a good man. History shows he was not always good. I wonder if Muslims know the real story about Muhammad.

The ideas of Jesus change over time.  People’s beliefs about him change too.  

The world is changing fast.  Many people want new ideas.  Old ideas stay, but they may not be strong.  Many Christians will want to learn more about Jesus.  They will want to know what he really taught.

It may take a long time, but people will go back to Jesus’ original ideas.  They will take away ideas that came later.  This will happen slowly.

This change will be big.  People will worship like they did in Jesus’ time.  The church will be strong.

But there will be fewer different kinds of Christians.  Everyone will believe the same things.

This has happened before.  People were mean to Christians.  But then the Roman Empire became Christian.

This change will happen in Christianity too.

The book *The Jungle* shows how people can be selfish. They only want good things for themself. They do not care about the people around them. The book shows this in many ways. The people who own the big factories only want to make more money. They do not care if people get hurt. Upton Sinclair writes, "The line of the buildings stood clear-cut and black against the sky; here and there out of the mass rose the great chimneys, with the river of smoke streaming away to the end of the world". This shows how bad the pollution is. The owners do not care about the people or animals who are hurt by the pollution. They do not care about the smoke from the factories or the waste from the animals.


The owners do not care about the workers. They want to save money. They make the workers work long hours. They can fire workers at any time. The people working in the factories have no rights. They have no one to help them.  The book says, "So from the top to bottom the place is simply a seething cauldron of jealousies and hatreds; there is no loyalty or decency anywhere about it, there is no place in it where a man counted for anything against a dollar". The workers are treated badly. They have no way to escape. The book says that the workers are like slaves.

Many writers use words to make people feel a special way about things.  F. Scott Fitzgerald uses many of these words in his book The Great Gatsby. He uses words in new ways to make people think about things differently. 


Fitzgerald uses colors in his book. He uses colors like gold, green, white, gray, and red. He uses these colors to make people feel something.

Fitzgerald uses white and gray to show that things are the same. White is clean and nice. Gray is old and faded.

Fitzgerald uses white and gray a lot at the start of the book. Daisy and Jordan wear white. Nick wears white. Tom wears a white shirt. Everyone wears white. The only time people are not in white is at Gatsby's party.

Fitzgerald uses white and gray to show things that are not important. He says Nick goes "down the white chasms" of New York. Names at Gatsby's party are "gray names." Catherine's apartment is like a "white cake."

Fitzgerald uses white and gray to show that Daisy is not important. He says Daisy is in a "white roadster." This makes Daisy seem like just another thing.

Fitzgerald uses white and gray to show that Daisy is not special. He says Daisy has a "gray haze" on her fur. She wears a "white" dress.

San Diego has good weather for farming. Farmers grow many things there. They grow tomatoes, lemons, oranges, greens, squash, broccoli, herbs, peaches, berries, honey, and peppers. Many people want to buy food from farms that use no chemicals. There are many groups that sell food from these farms. People like to buy eggs and milk that come from farms that use no chemicals. Some farms let people visit and see how they grow food. They also let people walk and look at birds. This is good for the farms and for the people who visit. People can learn about farming and help the farm make money.

Farming without chemicals is good for plants and animals. It helps them to grow better. But, it can cost more money. It takes more work to keep pests away and to feed the plants. Some plants die because they are not strong enough. Small farms don't have as much money as big farms.

There are other things farmers can do to help animals. They can plant special plants, move animals to different places, and get rid of bad plants. These things also cost more money.

This story is about a farm in San Diego. It is next to a big forest. There are many plants and animals there, some are in danger. The farm was used for many years by people.

This farm is a good example of how to help animals and make money.

Culture is important in talks. Culture is not one thing. It is many things. It is not good to say all people from one place are the same. It is better to know how culture can make talks different. When you talk with people from another place, you see it like your own culture.

You can learn about another culture by looking at its history. You can also learn by seeing what it thinks about things. Do not judge another culture. Just try to understand it. In talks, you should follow the rules of the other culture. This is especially true if you are not strong in the talks. If you go to another place to talk, respect the ways they do things. This can help you talk better.

Culture is not just about countries. Companies have their own cultures too. Some companies work many hours. Others have more time off. You can see a company's culture in what people wear, how they talk, and how they work. Some companies help people give money to charity. Others do not.

American companies are different from each other. Some are very big, others are small. Some are in cities, others are in the country. This shows that even in one country, cultures can be different.

Values are important because they show why people do things. If a culture values respect, people will not be mean to each other in talks. If a culture values getting a good deal, people will not give up easily.

Before you talk to someone, learn about their culture. This can help you talk better. But it is also good to get to know the person you are talking to.

The writer say, "People who do not believe in God are fools." This is from a part of the Bible called Psalm 14. It is also the start of an argument by a man named St. Anselm about God. Another writer, St. Thomas Aquinas, also thinks God exists. To know which argument is better, we must think both men believe in the same God. We can not talk about a different God.

Both men say good things. But neither gives a complete reason to believe in God.

First, we look at Anselm’s idea. Anselm says we find God by looking inside ourselves. He says because we can think about God, God must exist. We do not need to look outside ourselves for proof.

This is like faith. Faith is believing something even if we can not see it. Anselm says we can know God is real just by thinking about him.

Thomas Aquinas has a different idea. He says we can prove God exists with reason, not just faith. He gives five reasons why God must exist. Each reason is like a puzzle piece. If you have all the pieces but one, you know the missing piece is there.

Thomas says we can know God exists by looking at the world around us.

A long time ago, a prince was born. People now call him Buddha. He lived a good life, but he gave up the world. He found peace, and his ideas made Buddhism. Buddhism is very old.

Now, Buddhism is different than when Buddha lived. This is true in Sri Lanka, where monks and people have a big water ceremony. Buddha did not teach about this. Buddhism has changed a lot.

This change comes from many things. Some things are good and some are bad. Some come from inside Buddhism, and some come from outside. Buddhists call these things good or bad forces.

Buddhists believe in three things: Buddha, his teachings (Dhamma), and the community of Buddhists (Sangha). Buddha's teachings are in books called the Tripitaka. One book has stories. Another book has rules. The last book talks about deep ideas.

Buddhists believe life has suffering. They want to end this suffering. They believe they can do this by understanding these ideas and living a good life.

The United States and Mexico had a big problem for many years. It last for 57 years, from 1836 to 1893. The two countries had many fights. The biggest fight was the Mexican-American War. The United States won. The United States took Texas and land in the southwest. Many other problems happened between the two countries. The problems stopped just before World War One.

The fight started because Americans and Mexicans had different ideas. They had different ideas about religion, culture, and how to live. They also had different wants. This is like other countries that are close neighbors. Countries that share a border often have problems. The United States and Mexico are like other countries in history that have had big problems. 

Religion was a big problem. In the 1800s, Americans did not like Catholicism and kings.  This was like the Cold War, where the United States did not like communism. Both times, the United States had problems with another country because of ideas. The United States and Mexico did not trust each other because of their history.

There were many fights between the United States and Mexico. Most fights were about land. Robbers from the United States sometimes crossed into Mexico. Mexico and the United States used soldiers to stop the robbers.

Mexico became more dependent on the United States. The United States wanted to help Mexico’s economy. This made the problems smaller.

Fifteen years ago, I got very sick. I did not know I was sick. I was a nurse. I wanted to be a scientist or a reporter. But my family said I should be a nurse. They said, "You will always have a job. People always get sick."  So I became a nurse.


I was 46 years old and alone. I had no money. I could not work. I am still sick. I have lived on help from the government for 15 years. I have nothing. I am okay, but every day is hard. I am not safe or happy. I do not know what will happen next. But I know one thing: I could not have lived this long without my family and friends. When bad things happen, you need help.


Life has problems. Big problems and small problems. You can plan, but some things are too big to handle alone.


People in the United States say we need to stop depending on the government. They say it is not working. But I think we need to help each other. We need to trust each other. We need to ask for help when we need it.


People say the United States was built by strong, independent people. But the people who made this country strong were kind. They helped each other. They shared.

So, be ready for problems. I am. I have a kit with food, water, and supplies. I have flashlights and batteries. I have candles and matches. I have canned food. If you have land, grow your own food.  


But also, be nice to your neighbors.

Why do living things change over time? Are there rules that decide how they change? A long time ago, a scientist said we do not yet know how to explain how living things are made with math. Today, we are still trying to do that.

Scientists use math to understand how shells grow. They look at the shapes of seashells and use math to make models. Our study looks at how shells grow over time. We use pictures of seashells and math to understand how they change.

A shell is like a tube that spins around. Each part of the spin is called a whorl. Whorls are like steps on a spiral staircase. The center of the shell is called the columella. 

The size of the whorls can change. The line between the whorls is called a suture. The biggest whorl is the body whorl. The rest of the whorls make up the spire. The top of the spire is the apex and the bottom is the base. The animal lives inside the shell and comes out through an opening called the aperture.

We look at shells from different sides. The way we usually see a shell is with the opening facing us and the top pointing up. This is called the apertural view.


We can count the whorls by looking at the shell from the top. We draw a line to divide the shell in half and count the whorls.

A shell grows by adding new parts.  We can use math to track how the shell grows. We can look at the size and shape of each part and see how it changes.

Indonesia has had little change in baby and new born deaths in the last ten years.  The country is good at reaching some goals, like having safe water and good bathrooms. But, the country is not doing good enough to help mothers and babies.

Indonesia has more babies born with help from a doctor.  Now 72% of babies are helped by a doctor. But, this number includes midwives who can not help with problems during birth. Many mothers die from bleeding after birth.

Indonesia needs to do better with helping sick babies. Less babies are now getting help from a doctor when they are sick.

Indonesia does not have enough doctors. Only 4% of babies are born by surgery (C-section). This is less than it should be.

There are also problems in the cities and the countryside.  Cities have more doctors.  Rich people get more help than poor people.

To help more babies and mothers, Indonesia needs to do more than just special programs. Indonesia needs to make the whole health system better.

Programs are good because they focus on one problem.  They can help quickly.  But, programs can take money away from other parts of the health system.  Also, many programs can be confusing and make it hard to work together.

Victorian books are known for lots of detail. They often show the lives of rich people. Two books from this time, "Oliver Twist" and "Wuthering Heights", are different. They have mystery and strange things that make them special. This makes the people in the books more interesting. We learn more about why they act the way they do and how they feel. 

"Oliver Twist" and "Wuthering Heights" use mystery a lot. They do this with dreams and things that feel like dreams.  In "Oliver Twist", these strange things show us what is happening inside Oliver. They show us his pain and how he sees the world around him. 

In one part of "Oliver Twist", Oliver remembers being shot. It feels like a dream. He is trying to find help. 

The passage shows that Oliver did not control what happened. His body was hurt badly. He sees things like Sikes and Crackit, who hurt him. He feels pain all the time. The shooting was so bad that he does not feel anything else. He does not even see the person who takes him away. We can see that Oliver feels helpless. He does not try to stop what is happening. This shows that he is giving up.   

["Oliver Twist" also uses the mystery to show that Oliver has little control over his life. He doesn't get to choose what happens to him.  This makes him feel sad and defeated.


In "Wuthering Heights", the mystery is different.]

I work in a school after school program. I help kids with their school work. I am good at English and reading. One boy, Adrian, had trouble reading. He was in third or fourth grade. I tried to help him.

Adrian spoke English well. But he read words in a strange way. Some letters he knew, some he did not. I thought it was strange. Adrian was Latino, but he spoke good English. We had trouble.

One day, Adrian's mother came to the school. She only spoke Spanish. I spoke a little Spanish. We talked.

Then I understood. Adrian could read, but he did not know the English letters well. I think this helped him in the end.

This story shows a problem in schools. Some kids have trouble with language. It is not always easy to see the problem. Adrian spoke good English, but reading was hard for him.

What can we do? Adrian needed help with English reading. Other kids need more help. There is no one answer. We need many things.

One thing is to teach in two languages. This helps all kids. It is good for learning.

Some people say this is a waste of time. They say it does not help all kids. This is wrong. If we teach in two languages, all kids will learn.

We do not need all teachers to speak two languages. We need helpers who speak two languages.

Many people are told there is something bigger than them. Some go to church or temple to learn about it. Some find answers inside them. Many people take the religion of their parents. Some people say there is no more than what they see. We change our beliefs. We look for a way to feel good. We look for light in the dark.


My father said a cardinal was his favorite bird. We sat on the porch. Rain fell on the roof. He looked out at the rain. He was thin. His hair was less. He looked at the rain and did not look at me. I felt alone. I was afraid. I did not talk to him about missing him.  I hugged him. I sat close to him. We looked at the rain.


My father died in December.  He was sick for a long time. He died five days after my birthday. The sickness did not stop his pain. He lived longer than the doctors said he would. I did not know why. I did not pray. I did not believe in God.


I did not want to watch him die. I did not go to see him. I wanted to remember him as he was, not how he died. I knew him better than anyone.


I stayed in bed for three days. No one called me.

The Gothic story is old and new. This is what writer Ian Watt says in his book The Rise of the Gothic Novel. Gothic stories have been said to be bad and good. Some say they are not deep. Others say they show a scary beauty. The first Gothic story was The Castle of Otranto by Horace Walpole. Walpole used old stories and new ways to write. He made a new kind of story. 

Walpole used old ideas from plays and new ideas from stories about nature. He called his story "A Gothic Story." Gothic stories use old ideas from the Middle Ages. They use old ways of building and old beliefs.

Even when The Castle of Otranto was first written, the word "Gothic" was used for many things. Some people thought Gothic was old and not good. They thought new things were better. But the way Gothic stories are written is different. They let the reader know what the characters are thinking. This is why Gothic stories are still read today.

One important idea in Gothic stories is chivalry. Chivalry is about training to be a knight. It was important to Gothic writers because knights were brave and good. Gothic writers thought people today were not like knights. They wanted to show a better time.

Walpole wrote The Castle of Otranto when things were difficult in England. He was worried about the future. He may have thought that people in the past were better. In his story, a character named Frederic is a good example.

The story says Frederic is a prince. He has had bad things happen to him. He is brave and good. He is like a knight.

Supply chain management is the move of goods. It starts when a customer wants something. The goods go from raw materials to the customer. The words ‘supply chain management’ came from Keith Oliver in 1982. He was a helper for companies. He said this is how to plan, do, and watch over the move of goods. This helps companies give customers what they want fast and well. There are six big parts to a supply chain: make things, get supplies, keep things, pick places, move things, and use information. Managers use these six parts to help customers.

Making things is the first part. Making things is very important. It shows when, why, where, and how things are made. Managers need to know what people want to buy. They look at the market to see what people want. Once they know what people want, they can decide what to make and how much. 
Managers also need to decide where to make things. They pick a plant that is good for making a lot of things and making them well. They also need to make sure the things people want are made. After that, managers plan how much work to do and how to keep the machines good. Making things is very important. If things are not planned well, it can cost a lot of money and time later. 

The next part is getting supplies. This means making good choices about what a company can do and who to work with.  A company might have many ways to make one thing. Each way uses different things, workers, and skills. The manager has to pick the best way for each part of making the thing. Sometimes, managers give work to other companies. This is called outsourcing. Companies do this to make things faster, better, and cheaper.

This text talks about bad things that happen in some countries.

One country is Burma. People there do not like the leader. They had protests. The leader did bad things to the people. People were hurt and some died.  

This is not the only time this has happened. 

Many years ago, people in China had protests. The leader of China did bad things to the people.

Many years ago, bad things happened in Rwanda.  People killed other people.

Hitler, a leader a long time ago, did many bad things to people.

This text says that some leaders are bad and hurt people.

Duke Ellington make good music in jazz. He play music for many years. This make him good at making music for his band. Ellington play piano, but he not play much on some songs. He good at making songs with lots of parts.  He make songs for singers to sing alone and songs for all the band to play.  He also make the band sound good together. Ellington good at making music that sound new and different.

A book about music say Ellington use voice like an instrument. A song called "Creole Love Call" show this. He use voice to make song sound interesting, not just singing words. Ellington also good at making songs for his singers. This song go slow. It have six parts. 

The first part has voice and woodwind. The voice start slow and then sound rougher. The second part has trumpet that sound soft and play notes long. The third part has clarinet play fast and high. The fourth part has all the band play like the first part. The fifth part is loud.  The reeds play fast and high, and the brass and drums play slow. The sixth part is like the first part. The voice sound deep and rough. 

Ellington use voice like an instrument in many songs. In another song called "Hot and Bothered", he use trumpet and voice to make interesting sounds together. In "It Don't Mean a Thing," he use trombone to play the first part of the song.

Ellington good at making music that sound new and different.

She want something. This want was strong. It start when she was fourteen. The want was still there when she was seventeen. Now, she want a person, not a thing. But, she no like boys. Some boys like her. They try to talk to her, but she no care. She think about this a lot. She try to find a reason why she not like boys. She think about this for years. But, she no find a good answer. So she live her life, asking herself why.

Her home was usually peaceful. Her parents were good. They no fight. They no fight with her much. They only fight about her being independent. She was the daughter of calm people, but she was very fun. She was nice and people like her.

Today was not peaceful. She walk around her house. She want to do something, but she no know what. She hear her mother scream from the kitchen. She run to the kitchen. “Mom? Mom, what wrong?” Her mother was on the floor. She hurt. “Ouch… sweet - ty, I... need you to go to the hospital.” Her mother was in a lot of pain. “Okay Mom, tell me where to take you.”  Her mother point. The daughter was happy she was strong. She carry her mother to the car. She put her in the back and drive to the hospital.

At the hospital, it smell like medicine and sickness. The daughter was scared, but she help her mother. She carry her inside and call for help. Doctors come. They put her mother on a bed and take her away. The daughter wait and worry.

Her mother fall off a step stool. She try to get a vase.

This study looked at if eating a “Mediterranean Diet” (Med diet) helps keep women healthy. The Med diet has lots of plants, good fats, fish, and less of bad fats and meats. It is good for the heart.

Before, studies showed that the Med diet helps people live longer and have better heart health. This study looked at women only and saw if it helped prevent heart attacks and strokes.

The study looked at over 70,000 women for 20 years. The women told the scientists what they ate often. The scientists checked if the women had heart attacks or strokes. 

The scientists found that women who ate more like the Med diet had less heart attacks and strokes. This means the Med diet is good for women’s hearts.

In two thousand seven, the United States had a big money problem. Many people lost their jobs. Prices for homes went down. Many big companies had many problems. This problem is still here today. We must ask: how did this happen? How can we stop it? The problem was made by bad choices from people in charge. They made banks give out bad loans. The banks were not strong. Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac made bad loans into other things. When people could not pay back the loans, the banks had no money. This made the whole country’s money problem worse.  
The money problem started in nineteen ninety nine. President Clinton wanted to be president again. He wanted people to like him. So, he made it easy for banks to give out loans. This made the bad loans problem start. A man named Steven Holmes wrote in the New York Times in nineteen ninety nine: “Fannie Mae, the biggest company that helps people get home loans, is under pressure to give more loans to poor people.  They also want to make more money. But this could be a big problem if the economy gets bad.” He was right. Bad loans led to a big problem in the economy. 
Many things caused the money problem. New kinds of loans were made. These loans were hard to understand. People used too much money to buy homes. This made the problem worse when home prices went down. 
In two thousand seven, the five biggest banks in America had four trillion dollars in bad loans. This was thirty percent of all the money in America. Some banks had to sell themselves for very little money. Some banks closed. Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac were in big trouble and the government had to take over.

Ah, exposition.  That place in your story where you show your writer's skill and amaze your readers with your storytelling.  Or the part where your readers get bored and close the book.  Dr. Merlin has been known to shout at her monitor when she finds herself stuck in Too Much Information, and not even in the fun way.

Exposition is not your friend.

My readers already know the basic writing tip, "Show, don't tell," but Dr. Merlin still stumbles into long passages of text where nothing happens, or worse, too much. Exposition is like a little voice in your ear that says to get the history out of the way to get to the good parts.

Exposition means telling the audience what happened, usually in simple words.  In a movie, the exposition happens when one character tells another a lot of information, like in "The Rime of the Ancient Mariner."  In fiction, the writer is doing the telling.

Here's an example.  Imagine you're reading a story and you are told that the main character met her love at a certain place and time, that they had a big wedding, and that her husband was killed in front of her. You wouldn't want to read two pages about this, with both characters only getting two lines of dialogue each. You would expect the writer to spend time on the husband's character, showing how much he loved his wife through his words and actions. You would also expect the heroine to show how much his presence changed and improved her life.

A good introduction to the husband's character would let you feel connected to him and understand why his death is so important. It would also tell you more about the heroine: what she saw in him, how deep their bond was, clues about her thoughts, beliefs, and dreams as shown through his eyes, and so on. You would mourn his death with her, and that would make you care more about her.

In short, you would want more than just the bare bones of the story: "They met, they married, he died." As a writer, you need to add the details and make the story come alive.

Sometimes it is tempting to rush past certain things.  Maybe you're introducing a new character and you know he used to be in the Air Force, now he works the night shift at a gas station, he's been married twice, has no kids, likes to go fishing on the weekends, secretly wants to own the gas station someday, and had Eggs Benedict for breakfast.

I watch two news shows from Columbus, Ohio. The first show was NBC 4. It was live this morning, August 13, 2011. The first big story was about a man in Ashley, Ohio. He hurt his wife. The man's name was Shad Hostettler. They showed his picture. He looked bad. They did not say the wife's name. They talked about the story for two minutes. They said he hurt his wife many times. He was in jail. I think they talked about this story for the right amount of time.

The next story was about a man named Travis Buyers. He was 18 years old. He was shot this morning in Sharon Woods. He was very hurt. The police did not know who did it. They were looking for the person. This story was short. I think the news team did not talk about it long because he was black. I have seen this before. The news does not talk much about black people when they are hurt. If a white person is hurt, the news talks a lot about it.

The next story was about a helicopter. A bullet hit it. The police think a man shot it. They want to find the man. They are giving five thousand dollars for a tip.

The next story was about the weather. They said it would rain on Saturday. It would be hot this weekend.

They also talked about a store robbery. A man robbed a store on Clime Road. He was black. He wore a hoodie. He was tall and thin. I think they talked too much about his race.

They also talked about a man named Rene Rodriguez. He sold drugs. He was from Texas. He went to jail for a long time. They said he was Hispanic. I do not think that was important to the story.

Brothers have a strong bond. This bond is special. It has many feelings: love, joy, envy, and badness. Brothers know each other best. They see themselves when they look at their brother. When things are bad, the bond is strong. It can be good or bad. These feelings are strong. They cost a lot.

It is hard to understand these feelings. But we must deal with them. When you see your brother, you see yourself. You see who you really are. Your actions tell us who you are.

The story "The Scarlet Ibis" shows this bond. Two brothers have many feelings. They go on a sad trip. Pride and sadness are strong. Only one brother lives. The story shows how the main character feels. It shows his brother. It shows how he sees the world. These things make him do things.


The main character has one big feeling: pride. He wants to teach his brother things. He wants to play with him. His brother is sick. He is weak. He cannot do these things.  The main character is sad. He is angry. He even thinks about hurting his brother. But when his brother smiles, he feels better. He loves his brother.

The brain is very complex. It works like a computer. But it is more than just a computer. We learn about the brain by using words to describe it. We say it is like a wax tablet, then like paper, then like a book. Now we say it is like a computer. We must remember that these words are just ways to talk about the brain. They are not perfect.

The brain takes in information from our senses. We see, hear, touch, smell, and taste. This information is changed into signals the brain can use. The brain then works on these signals. It uses rules to put the information together.

When we see a black box on a white background, our brain uses simple information to figure out what it is. It sees the color, the shape, and where the edges are. This is called bottom-up processing. But our brain also uses what it already knows. It might know that a black box is more likely than a hole in the white background. This is called top-down processing.

The brain decides what is important. It uses a filter to choose which information to pay attention to. We see many things, but we do not notice them all. For example, we see each blade of grass, but we do not notice each one. We may notice our name, even in a noisy room.

Information must be stored in the brain. There are different kinds of memory: sensory, working, and long-term.

Information is first stored in sensory memory. Then it goes to working memory. This memory lasts for a short time. Long-term memory is where we store information for a long time.

There are many ways to study how the brain works. Some people study how people remember things. Others study computers. Others study the brain itself. One way to think about how knowledge is stored in the brain is the semantic network model. This model says that ideas are like points. These points are connected by lines. The lines show how ideas are related.

Aldous Huxley shows the bad parts of new technology and the way money rules in his story Brave New World. People in this story like to be part of a group more than they like to be alone. They are taught to be happy all the time. The people in the story are like pieces in a big game. They have to follow one way of thinking, the way the World Controller says. If you look at the story using ideas from Marx, you see that Huxley was worried about the way these things are working. He uses words like "same" and "thing" a lot. This shows that Huxley thinks his story is about problems in the way money worked in his time.
Money is a joke in this story. People are not allowed to see the real way money works. They only care about getting things for themselves. This is how people in power keep control of the workers, which is a big idea in Marx's ideas. The people in the story are not allowed to think for themselves. They are told to buy things and have fun all the time. This is how the World Controller controls them. 
Strong people control the weak people. The people in charge do not care about the people who work for them. The poor people do not know that they are being controlled. They think the system is good. The rich people know, but they do not care. This is how it works in Brave New World.
People do not have real relationships with each other. They do not care about each other. Huxley might be saying that new technology and money take away people's freedom. People do not love each other. They do not feel strong emotions. They just talk about each other's bodies. People are happy with the way things are. This shows that money is controlling people.

I study at University Park. I have been here for two years. Many students, like me, have trouble getting around. My first year, I lived in East Halls. It is far from the center of campus.

Going to classes in places like Willard building was a long walk. It could take 25 minutes, especially if the weather was bad. I talked to a grown-up who went to school here. He said that the East Halls used to be far from the rest of the school.

Now there are buildings and sports fields there. As the school gets bigger, it is hard to get around. What is the best way to move around? On a school, it is a bike. But only a bike is not enough. Students need to ride them, and the school needs to be good for bike riders.

I talk to a friend who rides a bike again. He said that he does not know why he stopped. “Bikes are good,” he said. “A few years ago, it was not cool to ride a bike, but it is the best way to get around.” Bikes are good for your body. They are the best way to travel.

I live off campus. It is far from the center of school. The best thing I did was to buy a bike. I go to class in Thomas building. It is a long walk.

Riding a bike takes five minutes. The problem is Pollock Road is not easy to ride on. You can walk, but I am too busy. If I did not have a bike, I would have to walk.

Walking to Thomas every day takes 30-40 minutes. That is over two hours every week. I do not have that time.
